Package com.tcs.entity

Class Vehicle

java.lang.Object
com.tcs.entity.Vehicle
@Entity public class Vehicle extends Object
Entity representing a vehicle insured under a policy. Each vehicle is linked to an underwriter and contains insurance-related details.
